Rotiferos de la Patagonia Argentina nuevos para SudamericaThe presence of Squatinella rostrum rostrum (Schmarda), Euchlanis oropha Gosse and Lecane (Monostyla) lunaris f. perplexa (Ahlstrom) in the Argentine's provinces of Rio Negro and Chubut is reported with descriptions and figures. The three taxa are new for the South American fauna.